%h1 Coworking Terms and Member Agreement
%h2 Membership
%p
  Start Charlotte coworking membership does not creates a
  tenancy, but a prepaid usage license to use the provided
  amenities on a monthly basis.  This license may be
  cancelled by either Start Charlotte or the licensee at
  any time.
%h2 Member Conduct
%p
  All members shall adhere to the rules of conduct
  at all times. Failure to do so will result in a stern
  talking-to, and possible revocation of coworking
  privileges.
%p
